description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Confidence Building Row' from the channel Mike Dostal.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Competitor vibe.
The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn. The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record..
The technique difficulty is Advanced.
The effort required is Extreme.

Original workout description: Try this workout to help you develop a new level of confidence in what you can do with Mike and Mac.
Max rhythm: 34, Format: HIIT...
